===Etymology===
An irregular romanization of {{etyl|zh|en}} {{m|zh|陝西||[Land] [[west|West]] of the [[Shan]] [[pass|Pass]]|tr=Shǎnxī}}, with the first syllable from the [[Gwoyeu Romatzyh]] system and the second from [[pinyin]], in order to distinguish it from the province of {{m|zh|山西||[Land] [[west|West]] of the [Taihang] [[mountain|Mountains]]|tr=Shānxī}} in atonal spelling. When tone marks are present, the single-A ''[[Shǎnxī]]'' is preferred.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ʃɑːnˈʃiː/|/ˈʃænˈʃiː/|lang=en}}

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}

# A [[province]] of [[China]] with [[its]] [[capital]] at [[Xi'an]] and [[including]] the [[Wei River]] [[valley]] and the [[fertile]] [[southern]] [[half]] of the [[Ordos]] [[loop|Loop]], [[comprising]] [[much]] of the [[Loess Plateau]].

